1
00:00:58,016 --> 00:01:00,992
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,992 --> 00:01:02,962
=Episode 1=

3
00:01:02,962 --> 00:01:06,984
(My Husband is Missing)

4
00:01:07,902 --> 00:01:09,984
(Gu Mansion)

5
00:01:10,048 --> 00:01:13,958
(Gu Mansion)

6
00:01:22,208 --> 00:01:23,888
(Brother Gu Zhaoxi's Spirit Tablet)

7
00:01:50,176 --> 00:01:52,032
(Brother Gu Zhaoxi's Spirit Tablet)

8
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,560
Zhaoxi.

9
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:27,919
Stop.

10
00:02:47,584 --> 00:02:49,644
(Crown Prince, Yin Zhou)

11
00:02:57,479 --> 00:02:58,800
You may go in peace.

12
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,639
The bamboo forest outside
is bandit-infested.

13
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,800
The court has sent men to kill them.

14
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:06,319
You are avenged.

15
00:03:07,039 --> 00:03:08,840
(Eldest Young Master of the Gu family)
I'll find your remains

16
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:12,400
(Gu Chaosheng)
and make you have a proper burial.

17
00:03:27,168 --> 00:03:30,048
(Yuluo, Xuanji Pavilion)

18
00:03:30,272 --> 00:03:35,136
(Virtue of Heaven and Earth)

19
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:38,840
Master, all our men have returned.

20
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,520
(Xuan Qing, Xuan Unit of Xuanji Pavilion)
No news of Master Zhaoxi.

21
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,159
Do you really want...?

22
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,319
You and Master Zhaoxi
aren't married yet.

23
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,719
There's no need to go this far.

24
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,960
Where's your young mistress?

25
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,360
Not here to offer incense
for her husband?

26
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:11,584
Chaosheng, my husband isn't dead.

27
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:14,080
Why speak of offering incense?

28
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:34,759
How dare you are in red
to desecrate Zhaoxi's memorial?

29
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:37,000
Guards! Seize her!

30
00:05:44,096 --> 00:05:46,368
(Brother Gu Zhaoxi's Spirit Tablet)

31
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,480
Let all present bear witness.

32
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:59,040
From this day forth, I, Gu Yuluo,
take Gu Zhaoxi as my husband.

33
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:01,240
Death won't part us.

34
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:07,040
I refuse to acknowledge
his death until I find him.

35
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,240
No matter he is alive or dead,
bring him to me.

36
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:50,199
Impressive skills, Your Highness.
But you left no survivors.

37
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:52,920
This will hinder future investigations.

38
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:55,519
Survivors? I kept this one.

39
00:06:58,208 --> 00:06:59,712
(Virtue of Heaven and Earth)

40
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:10,720
Why involve yourself
in this mess, Master?

41
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:16,199
Is it for Master Zhaoxi?
Or do you want to be Pavilion Master?

42
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:20,519
Zhaoxi's fate remains unknown,
but some have revealed their ambitions.

43
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,240
Is this memorial truly for mourning?

44
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,160
Or just to declare him dead?

45
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:28,680
Things have long changed
in the Gu family.

46
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:30,439
But Master Zhaoxi...

47
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:36,240
Without him, how will you
control the Gu family?

48
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:37,879
Keep searching.

49
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:41,720
If you can't find him,
find someone who resembles him.

50
00:07:43,279 --> 00:07:47,920
Disguise is the specialty
of our Xuanji Pavilion after all.

51
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,759
Why let that man escape, Master?

52
00:07:53,199 --> 00:07:55,680
Aren't you afraid
he'll report to his superiors?

53
00:07:57,839 --> 00:08:00,879
It doesn't matter. Do your duty.

54
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:01,680
Yes.

55
00:08:49,088 --> 00:08:54,084
(Gu Mansion)

56
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,799
Thanks for leading.

57
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,200
(Tianlan, Crown Prince's secret guard)
Just as you predicted.

58
00:09:16,544 --> 00:09:17,920
(Gu Mansion)

59
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,360
This man is useless now.
Shall we keep him?

60
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:25,679
Useless people

61
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:27,360
get killed.

62
00:09:30,368 --> 00:09:33,120
(Three days later)

63
00:09:36,384 --> 00:09:37,285
(Zuixian Building)

64
00:09:56,879 --> 00:09:59,000
Gu Zhaoxi's wife...

65
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,240
Who else would do something like that?

66
00:10:01,399 --> 00:10:02,919
Trouble is brewing.

67
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:06,879
Since the Crown Prince's death,
the Emperor hasn't held court for days.

68
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:10,360
Now, even Gu Zhaoxi...

69
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,759
That jinx.

70
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:17,799
That jinx is here again.

71
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:18,559
Yeah.

72
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,000
Master.

73
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:41,759
Chaosheng
has been unusually quiet lately.

74
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:43,720
Any news of Master Zhaoxi?

75
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:49,399
Those lookalikes
you found are unsatisfactory.

76
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,759
Any new ones?

77
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:53,480
Not yet.

78
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,639
Did you fail to find any,

79
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,600
or did you not even try?

80
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:05,000
What brings you here so suddenly?

81
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:11,360
Because someone taking my pay
can't even find a lookalike.

82
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:18,080
You suspect the Gu family
took part in the assassination.

83
00:11:18,639 --> 00:11:20,919
Could Gu Zhaoxi be the mastermind?

84
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:24,320
Or was he killed afterwards?

85
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,480
And his wife, Mrs. Gu...

86
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,039
The people all over the city
praises her devotion.

87
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,559
But she is having fun here.

88
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:34,559
They say Gu Zhaoxi
was constantly bedridden.

89
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:36,120
Few ever saw him.

90
00:11:36,679 --> 00:11:40,000
His wife doubted his death
and searched for him secretly.

91
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:42,000
That's how I obtained a portrait.

92
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:46,320
But she is seeking a replacement.

93
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,240
In that case,

94
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,840
I'd like to meet

95
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,440
this young madam.

96
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:05,879
Are you going to...

97
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,000
Such a perfect opportunity

98
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,960
must be used to thoroughly investigate

99
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:17,480
the Gu family's intentions.

100
00:12:17,799 --> 00:12:19,840
Master, I've discovered

101
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:23,240
Mrs. Gu comes
from the Gus' Xuanji Pavilion.

102
00:12:23,919 --> 00:12:27,000
(Their mission is to gather intelligence
and carry out missions.)

103
00:12:27,399 --> 00:12:29,360
(The members are unfathomable.)

104
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:40,279
(Can two people truly be
so identical in this world?)

105
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,320
(Or...)

106
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,808
The Gu family specializes in disguise.

107
00:12:47,879 --> 00:12:50,559
They replaced your coachman
and tried to assassinate you.

108
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:53,639
They even created a face
identical to yours at their place.

109
00:12:54,279 --> 00:12:56,799
I wonder what they are plotting.

110
00:12:58,639 --> 00:12:59,720
Investigate them,

111
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:01,960
and then we'll know.

112
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,399
Yes.

113
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:14,440
What did you think of that dancer?

114
00:13:14,759 --> 00:13:15,559
Beat him!

115
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:30,600
Master.

116
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:35,320
Destiny governs all lives. We, too,
are not masters of our own will.

117
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,559
We can't follow our heart.

118
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:39,639
What right do we have
to meddle in the fates of others?

119
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:03,600
Zhaoxi.

120
00:14:09,039 --> 00:14:10,919
Don't be afraid. I'll bring you home.

121
00:14:27,639 --> 00:14:30,639
Thank you. I came
to the capital to visit my relatives.

122
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:33,720
Bandits robbed me
of all my traveling funds.

123
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,000
That's why...

124
00:14:49,399 --> 00:14:50,919
If you have nowhere to go,

125
00:14:51,799 --> 00:14:53,840
why not return with me
and secure employment?

126
00:14:55,159 --> 00:14:58,039
I'll provide
for all your daily necessities,

127
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:01,559
settle your debts
and arrange for your family's welfare.

128
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:05,879
Upon completing my task,
I'll reward you handsomely.

129
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,360
What task?

130
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:22,480
Be my husband.

131
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:33,088
(Fufeng Pavilion)

132
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,480
How long has he bathed?

133
00:15:40,799 --> 00:15:43,200
As you ordered, it's been four hours.

134
00:15:44,279 --> 00:15:47,799
This man is suspicious.
Please think carefully.

135
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:50,399
Of course I know.

136
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:55,039
How could two people bear
such resemblance in this world?

137
00:15:55,679 --> 00:15:57,720
And he happened
to show up at this moment.

138
00:15:58,159 --> 00:15:58,960
But...

139
00:16:01,159 --> 00:16:02,879
We live by the blade.

140
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:05,720
Why dread its edge?

141
00:16:34,639 --> 00:16:37,000
Xuan Qing must have already told you.

142
00:16:37,039 --> 00:16:39,399
I need you to impersonate
my husband, Gu Zhaoxi.

143
00:16:40,279 --> 00:16:41,519
Once I find him

144
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:45,480
or confirm his death, you may depart.

145
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:51,960
(I've heard the Gu family
has four young masters.)

146
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,919
(How can I get past them?)

147
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,240
Even I'm not shy.

148
00:17:22,079 --> 00:17:23,480
Why are you shy?

149
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:26,440
We're going to play husband and wife.

150
00:17:28,119 --> 00:17:29,000
Besides,

151
00:17:30,079 --> 00:17:31,359
this is my room.

152
00:17:41,839 --> 00:17:44,640
Zhaoxi has been frail
and bedridden since childhood.

153
00:17:45,279 --> 00:17:46,839
His brothers trade far afield.

154
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,640
He's not very close to his siblings.

155
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,359
So,

156
00:17:52,359 --> 00:17:53,839
he carries medicinal scents.

157
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,279
Starting today,

158
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:01,079
you'll soak in herbal baths
for four hours daily.

159
00:18:02,839 --> 00:18:05,200
Since you resemble him quite a bit,

160
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:24,160
I'll perfect your resemblance.

161
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:34,799
Prolonged herbal baths
may harm your health.

162
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:38,000
You can get changed now.

163
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:40,559
Lady, perhaps you should leave?

164
00:18:42,799 --> 00:18:43,920
Still calling me "Lady"?

165
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:48,079
Shouldn't you call me dear?

166
00:19:42,816 --> 00:19:47,879
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

167
00:19:48,416 --> 00:19:53,737
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

168
00:19:54,304 --> 00:20:00,932
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

169
00:20:00,932 --> 00:20:05,696
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

170
00:20:05,696 --> 00:20:08,032
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

171
00:20:08,032 --> 00:20:14,732
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

172
00:20:14,732 --> 00:20:21,504
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

173
00:20:21,504 --> 00:20:28,640
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

174
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:33,024
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

175
00:20:33,024 --> 00:20:35,648
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

176
00:20:35,648 --> 00:20:42,282
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

177
00:20:42,282 --> 00:20:48,832
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

178
00:20:48,832 --> 00:20:55,956
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

179
00:20:56,046 --> 00:21:00,416
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

180
00:21:00,416 --> 00:21:03,124
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

181
00:21:03,124 --> 00:21:09,024
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

182
00:21:09,664 --> 00:21:15,652
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

